<th>Middle Irish [831-832,833,837-840]<sup id="cite_ref-CMT168-CELT_13-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-CMT168-CELT-13">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup></th>
<th>Modern English<sup id="cite_ref-CMT168Eng-CELT_14-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-CMT168Eng-CELT-14">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup>
</th></tr>

<tr align="center">
<td>Ni accus bith nombeo baid:<br />sam cin blatha,<br />beti bai cin blichda,<br /><br />
<p>mna can feli<br />fir gan gail.<br />Gabala can righ...<br /><br />
feda cin mes.<br />Muir can toradh.<br /><br />
